snippet.title: FrogFlop - Trailer
snippet.description:
In Floppy's Great Leap, you play as Floppy the frog, aiming to reach the highest peak. Jump and climb through challenging levels in this 2D pixel art adventure. ne wrong move and you could find yourself back at the bottom!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2490140/FrogFlop/
